data.post_title: Google launches URL2Video AI tool that can convert webpage into a video
data.post_body: Google has released a new Artificial Intelligence (AI) powered tool that can convert a web page into a short video. The URL2Video tool requires only the website URL of the website. The tool extracts texts, images, or videos argon with the design styles like font, colour and layout from the HTML sources. While organising the virtual assets into sequences of shots, the tool maintains a look and feel similar to the source page.

data.post_title: How to master your competitive programming skills
data.post_body: The art of making machines work as per your instructions is simply called programming. To survive the coming era of continuous advancements, programmers need to master their competitive coding skills.
